'''飓风伊欧凯'''（-{zh-cn:{{lang|en|Hurricane Ioke}}; zh-tw:{{lang|en|Hurricane Ioke}}; zh-hk:{{lang|en|Hurricane Ioke}}; zh-mo:{{lang|pt|Furacão Ioke}}}-）又名'''台风伊欧凯'''（-{zh-cn:{{lang|en|Typhoon Ioke}}; zh-tw:{{lang|en|Typhoon Ioke}}; zh-hk:{{lang|en|Typhoon Ioke}}; zh-mo:{{lang|pt|Tufão Ioke}}}-），是有纪录以来中太平洋出现的最强[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。作为[[2006年太平洋飓风季|2006年太平洋飓风季]]期间中太平洋形成的首场风暴，伊欧凯创下多项纪录，不但纵横太平洋达17天之久，而且强度先后3度达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的[[五级太平洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]标准。

气旋由[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]以南较远处的[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]发展而成，由于[[海面温度|水温]]较高，[[风切变|风切变]]极少，还有良好的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]推波助澜，伊欧凯迅速增强，在48小时内就从热带低气压强化成四级飓风。8月22日晚，风暴快速弱化成二级飓风，然后从[[约翰斯顿环礁|约翰斯顿环礁]]上空经过。两天后，气旋又因外界环境有利而得以[[快速增强|快速增强]]，于8月25日达到五级飓风标准并在不久后穿越[[国际日期变更线|国际日期变更线]]。伊欧凯继续向西行进，其强度反复波动，于8月31日以风力时速249公里强度从[[威克岛|威克岛]]附近经过。风暴接下来转朝西北方向移动，之后又转向北上，并在此期间逐渐弱化，于9月6日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。系统残留加速向东北前进，最终进入[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]上空。

无论是在飓风还是台风时期，伊欧凯都没有对中太平洋和西太平洋任何人口常住地区构成影响。[[约翰斯顿环礁|约翰斯顿环礁]]有12人在风暴来袭期间躲进飓风掩体，他们估计气旋风速超过每小时160公里，对岛上树木构成破坏，但鸟类基本没有受到影响。台风在[[威克岛|威克岛]]构成中等程度破坏，部分建筑受损，房屋的屋顶被刮掉，损失总额约8800万美元（2006年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|88000000|2006}}}}美元），幸而所有军事人员均已撤离，岛上基础设施也都完好无损。伊欧凯的温带残留之后还在阿拉斯加州海岸沿线产生强烈[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，引起海滩侵蚀。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Ioke 2006 track.png}}
2006年8月中旬，[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]东南方向较远处海域催生出带有[[大气环流|下层环流]]的[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]。由于北面存在向西移动的强烈[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]，这股扰动天气几乎保持向正西方向移动，系统内的深层对流每天都在增长和消亡间拉锯。随着组织结构的缓慢改善，系统于8月20日清晨在[[檀香山|檀香山]]以南约1247公里洋面发展成第一{{lang|en|C}}号热带低气压。当时热带辐合带10°[[经度|经度]]范围内都没有关联对流。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | year = 2007 | title = 2006 Tropical Cyclones Central North Pacific | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306135254/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>气旋所在海域基本没有[[风切变|风切变]]，[[海面温度|海面温度]]又有28[[摄氏度|℃]]左右，两项因素都非常有利于强化<ref name="tcr" />，中太平洋飓风中心此时预计气旋会在4天内达到飓风强度下限，然后就会开始减弱<ref>{{cite report | author = Matsuda | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Depression One-C Discussion One | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.1.0608200252 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150201022353/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.1.0608200252 | archivedate = 2015-02-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。经过6小时的发展，低气压达到热带风暴标准<ref name="tcr" />，中太平洋飓风中心因此以“伊欧凯”（{{lang|en|Ioke}}），即[[夏威夷语|夏威夷语]]中的“乔伊斯”（{{lang|en|Joyce}}）为其命名<ref name="Ioke name">{{cite report | author = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.2.0608200853 | title = Tropical Storm Ioke Discussion Number 2 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2005-08-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184927/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.2.0608200853 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-03-18}}</ref>。气旋接下来快速强化，到8月20日晚已发展出[[中心密集云区|中心密集云区]]并开始形成[[风眼|风眼墙]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Nash | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Ioke Discussion Four | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.4.0608202049 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210334/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.4.0608202049 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，于8月21日清晨升级成飓风，这时距系统归类成热带低气压还只过了24小时<ref name="tcr" />。

伊欧凯继续向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向前进，对流稳步深化，风眼变得越来越层次分明，组成风眼墙的对流也不断深化<ref>{{cite report | author = Houston | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Ioke Discussion Seven | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303173932/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.7.0608211447 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.7.0608211447}}</ref>。受[[国际日期变更线|国际日期变更线]]附近的[[低压槽|锋面槽]]影响，飓风转向西北，并在经过一段时间的[[快速增强|快速增强]]后于8月22日在[[约翰斯顿环礁|约翰斯顿环礁]]东南方向约450公里海域达到风速每小时217公里强度，已达[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的四级飓风标准。在四级强度下保持约18小时后，<ref name="tcr" />伊欧凯的内层核心因西南向风切变而略遭扰乱<ref>{{cite report | author = Browning | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Ioke Discussion Twelve | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.12.0608222105 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194148/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.12.0608222105}}</ref>，风速很快就降至每小时约169公里。8月22日晚，风暴从约翰斯顿环礁以南约48公里洋面经过<ref name="tcr" />，风眼墙东北象限则在次日清晨经过<ref>{{cite report | author = Donaldson | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Ioke Discussion Thirteen | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222553/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.13.0608230245 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.13.0608230245 | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | archivedate = 2013-12-20}}</ref>。8月23日下午，飓风转向西进，然后因风切变减少而再度进入快速增强期。到8月24日时，伊欧凯已凝聚出宽37公里的闭合风眼墙<ref>{{cite report | author = Kodama | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Ioke Discussion Twenty | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203045/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.20.0608242050 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.20.0608242050}}</ref>，并于8月25日在夏威夷[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]西南偏西方向约1560公里海域达到[[五级太平洋飓风列表|五级飓风标准]]<ref name="tcr" />。

[[File:Ioke_2006-08-28_0130Z.jpg|thumb]]后，台风伊欧凯继续增强]]

保持五级飓风强度约18小时后<ref name="tcr" />，伊欧凯因[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]而略有减弱<ref>{{cite report | author = Burke | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Ioke Discussion Twenty-Five | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.25.0608260248 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213722/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.25.0608260248 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。8月26日完成眼墙置换周期后<ref name="disc26">{{cite report | author = Browning | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Ioke Discussion Twenty-Six | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183620/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.26.0608260919 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP2.CP012006.26.0608260919}}</ref>，气旋再度达到五级飓风标准。由于西侧的低压槽逐渐拉开距离，飓风前方得以形成副热带高压脊，促使伊欧凯向西南转向<ref name="tcr" />。外界总体环境依然非常有利于风暴保持较高强度，西北方向较远处的上层气旋产生利好外流的同时，也使得风切变一直很少，并且飓风行经洋面也总保持着比较高的水温<ref name="disc26" />。根据这些情况，[[地球物理流体动力学实验室|地球物理流体动力学实验室]]的飓风模型预计伊欧凯的风速会达到每小时350公里，最低气压低至860[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]）<ref>{{cite report | author = Geophysical Fluid Dynamics Laboratory | year = 2006 | title = GFDL Hurricane Ioke Prediction: 2006-08-31 00z | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://s35.photobucket.com/user/RattleMan/media/GFDL-860mb-191kt.png.html | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | format = PNG | via = Photobucket | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210428/http://i35.photobucket.com/albums/d178/RattleMan/GFDL-860mb-191kt.png}}</ref>。8月27日清晨，飓风气压降至915毫巴，并在不久后穿越国际日期变更线，成为风速每小时260公里的强劲台风<ref name="tcr" />。

[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]将进入西太平洋的伊欧凯归类为[[热带气旋等级|超級颱風]]，但这一认定不具备正式地位。进入西太平洋后，风暴强度在五级飓风标准下仍然保持了12小时，再于8月28日开始因北侧的高压脊导致内流增多而进入缓慢减弱阶段。<ref name="iokeatcr">{{cite report | author = [[联合台风警报中心|Joint Typhoon Warning Center]] | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/2006atcr/NWP_IO/StormNWP_IO/cp01.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110607051245/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/2006atcr/NWP_IO/StormNWP_IO/cp01.html | archivedate = 2011-06-07 | deadurl = yes | year = 2007 | title = Super Typhoon 01C | accessdate = 2011-06-07}}</ref><ref name="prog33">{{cite report | author = Alpha Forecast Team | year = 2006 | title = Typhoon Ioke Prognostic Reasoning NR 033 | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center}}</ref>8月29日，气旋沿副热带高压脊边缘行进，先是转朝西面移动，之后又转向西北偏西，其强度再一次达到五级飓风标准<ref name="iokeatcr" />。8月30日，[[气象厅_(日本)|日本气象厅]]估计伊欧凯达到[[最大持续风速|10分钟持续风速]]每小时195公里的最高强度<ref name="jma">{{cite report | author = [[气象厅_(日本)|Japan Meteorological Agency]] | year = 2006 | title = 2006 Western North Pacific Tropical Cyclones Best Track | accessdate = 2011-07-09 | url = http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/jma-eng/jma-center/rsmc-hp-pub-eg/Besttracks/bst2006.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110709143349/http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/jma-eng/jma-center/rsmc-hp-pub-eg/Besttracks/bst2006.txt | archivedate = 2011-07-09 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。当天下午，台风减弱至相当于四级飓风强度，再于8月31日以风力时速约249公里强度从[[威克岛|威克岛]]近海掠过<ref name="iokeatcr" />。

受风切变增多和干燥空气侵蚀的共同影响，到9月1日时，伊欧凯的风眼已被拉长并被云层阻挡<ref name="prog51">{{cite report | author = Bravo Forecast Team | year = 2006 | title = Typhoon Ioke Prognostic Reasoning NR 051 | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center}}</ref>，风暴于次日进入新一轮眼墙置换周期<ref name="prog55">{{cite report | author = Charlie Forecast Team | year = 2006 | title = Typhoon Ioke Prognostic Reasoning NR 055 | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center}}</ref>。9月2日，气旋以风速约每小时201公里强度从[[南鸟岛|南鸟岛]]以北约80公里洋面经过<ref>{{cite web | author = Hendricks | year = 2006 | title = Typhoon Ioke (01C) Advisory Number 56 | deadurl = yes | publisher = Guam National Weather Service | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/06090218 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025713/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/06090218 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。台风继续弱化，并围绕副热带高压脊逐渐转朝西北方向前进。受低压槽逐渐深化影响，气旋转朝西北偏北方向前进，之后又转向北上<ref name="prog61">{{cite report | author = Delta Forecast Team | year = 2006 | title = Typhoon Ioke Prognostic Reasoning NR 061 | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center}}</ref>，在日本以东数百公里海域降级成热带风暴。向东北方向加速后，伊欧凯开始失去热带天气系统特征，联合台风警报中心于9月5日宣布系统已转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。<ref name="iokeatcr" />不过，日本气象厅认为系统直到次日才减弱至台风强度以下，并且9月6日中午才转变成温带气旋。该机构继续追踪伊欧凯的温带残留，直至9月7日系统行进至[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]的[[阿留申群岛|阿留申群岛]]附近。<ref name="jma" />系统在逼近阿留申群岛期间又一次增强，风速达到飓风标准。9月8日，风暴残留进入[[白令海|白令海]]，然后在向东穿越阿留申群岛后进入[[阿拉斯加湾|阿拉斯加湾]]，最终于9月12日在[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]东南部附近消散。<ref name="mwl">{{cite report | author = George P. Bancroft | year = 2007 | title = Marine Weather Review—North Pacific Area September through December 2006 | publisher = NOAA National Center for Environmental Prediction | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://www.vos.noaa.gov/MWL/apr_07/northpacific.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130222020722/http://www.vos.noaa.gov/MWL/apr_07/northpacific.shtml | archivedate = 2013-02-22 | deadurl = yes | date =  }}</ref>

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:1890000_Wake_09.01.06_Ioke.png|thumb]]附近时对浪高、风速、风向、气压和气温产生的影响]]

=== 约翰斯顿环礁 ===
由于无法确知各岛上是否有人<ref>{{cite web|author=Office of the Federal Coordinator for Meteorology |year=2007 |title=Actions and Recommendations for the 61st Interdepartmental Hurricane Conference |accessdate=2016-03-18 |url=http://www.ofcm.gov/ihc07/web-61st-IHC-Booklet.pdf |page=115 |format=PDF |archivedate=2016-03-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170000/http://www.ofcm.gov/ihc07/web-61st-IHC-Booklet.pdf |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，中太平洋飓风中心于8月21日晚向没有常住人口的约翰斯顿环礁发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]，伊欧凯会在24小时后行进至距离该领地最近的位置<ref name="pa8">{{cite report | author1 = Kodama | author2 = Ballard | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Ioke Public Advisory Eight | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170823/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCPCP2.CP012006.8.0608212103 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCPCP2.CP012006.8.0608212103 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。当时有艘[[美国空军|美国空军]]船只和12名船员正在岛上，他们在固定船只后进入防飓风混凝土掩体躲避<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite news | last = Leone | first = Diana | title = Hawaiian-named storm hits Johnston Isle | archivedate = 2015-09-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2006/08/23/news/story01.html | publisher = Star Bulletin | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150912180820/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2006/08/23/news/story01.html | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | date = 2006-08-23}}</ref>。岛上没有气象观测站，但据这些船员估计，岛上的飓风强度狂风持续有6至8小时，热带风暴强度大风则持续了约27小时，最强阵风时速估计为每小时180到210公里。所有人员都在风暴期间安然度过，没有人员受伤，他们的船也只受到轻度破坏。伊欧凯的部分风眼从约翰斯顿环礁上空经过，导致岛上约15%的棕榈树顶端被风刮断，还有些铁木树被刮倒，不过岛上的鸟类基本未受影响。此外，飓风产生的强烈潮汐还将一段海堤及其邻近的道路冲毁。<ref name="tcr" />

=== 威克岛 ===
[[File:Ioke_2006-08-31_0205Z.jpg|thumb]]
面对台风威胁，夏威夷州威克岛有188至200名军事人员搭乘两架[[波音C-17环球霸王III|C-17运输机]]撤离，这也是该岛自[[1967年太平洋台风季|1967年]]台风莎拉过后首次全面撤离<ref name="829afpn">{{cite news | author = Andrew Leonhard | date = 2006-08-29 | title = Wake evacuated -- Airmen airlift 188 from Pacific Island | publisher = Air Force Print News | accessdate = 2012-10-14 | url = http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123026137 | archivedate = 2012-10-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121014113516/http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123026137 | deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated press]] | title = Wake Island evacuated as Super Typhoon Ioke closes in | year = 2006 | newspaper = Anchorage Daily News | accessdate = 2008-05-28 | url = http://dwb.adn.com/news/alaska/ap_alaska/story/8132157p-8024611c.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080528023150/http://dwb.adn.com/news/alaska/ap_alaska/story/8132157p-8024611c.html | archivedate = 2008-05-28 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。威克岛以东近海的一个浮标在伊欧凯直接从上空经过期间测得921.5毫巴的气压值<ref name="gp">{{cite web|author=Gary Padgett |year=2006 |title=Tropical Cyclone Summary for August 2006 |accessdate=2016-03-18 |url=http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2007/summ0608.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219194420/http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2007/summ0608.htm |archivedate=2012-02-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。台风从该岛以北近海经过前，风速计测得飓风强度狂风，最强阵风时速达到160公里后风速计就停止了工作<ref name="wimo" />。估计岛上持续风速达到每小时249公里，阵风时速高达310公里<ref>{{cite news | author = Chris Vadnais | date = 2006-09-13 | title = Teams fly to Wake Island to assess damage | publisher = Air Force Print News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017220912/http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123026973 | accessdate = 2012-10-17 | url = http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123026973 | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月31日上午9点06分，岛上测得934毫巴（百帕）的最低气压值<ref name="wimo">{{cite report|author=NOAA |year=2006 |title=Meteorological Observations for Wake Island on August 31, 2006 |accessdate=2009-07-27 |url=http://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/data_menu.shtml?bdate=20060830&bdate_Month=7&edate=20060831&edate_Month=7&unit=1&shift=&stn=1890000+Wake+Island%2C+U.+S.+TRUST+TERRITORY&type=Meteorological+Observations&format=View+Data |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727091616/http://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/data_menu.shtml?bdate=20060830&bdate_Month=7&edate=20060831&edate_Month=7&unit=1&shift=&stn=1890000%20Wake%20Island%2C%20U.%20S.%20TRUST%20TERRITORY&type=Meteorological%20Observations&format=View%20Data |archivedate=2009-07-27|deadurl=no }}</ref>。预计台风会在威克岛产生高达5.5米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，浪高则有12米，而该岛最高点的海拔高度也只有6.1米。此外，暴雨还令岛上多幢建筑被淹，风暴过去数天后积水还有0.6米深。<ref name="afd">{{cite web | author = Rob Tebben | year = 2006 | title = Ioke on Wake Island | publisher = Air Force Weather Observer | accessdate = 2013-02-16 | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130216230416/http://www.afweather.af.mil/shared/media/document/AFD-061108-011.pdf | url = http://www.afweather.af.mil/shared/media/document/AFD-061108-011.pdf | archivedate = 2013-02-16}}</ref>

伊欧凯的狂风令威克岛电网受到大范围破坏，大部分建筑物和后备发电机的输电线缆受损。狂风和风暴潮共同影响，致使全岛70%的建筑受损，许多屋顶受到中等程度破坏。所有低洼地区不是充满海水就是被沙子掩埋，岛上的自来水供应也相应中断。<ref name="afd" />威克岛通讯中断，卫星天线和光缆都被摧毁<ref name="afpn917">{{cite news | author = Chris Vadnais | date = 2006-09-17 | title = Airmen piece together Wake Island connectivity puzzle | publisher = Air Force Print News | accessdate = 2012-10-18 | archivedate = 2012-10-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121018001123/http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123027270 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123027270}}</ref>。基础设施受到台风重创，不过程度依然低于预期，而且大都还能修复<ref name="afd2">{{cite news | author = Chris Vadnais | date = 2006-09-15 | title = Airmen Add Up Damage at Wake Island | publisher = Air Force Print News | accessdate = 2014-12-20 | archivedate = 2014-12-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141220012238/http://www.af.mil/News/ArticleDisplay/tabid/223/Article/129764/airmen-add-up-damage-at-wake-island.aspx | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.af.mil/News/ArticleDisplay/tabid/223/Article/129764/airmen-add-up-damage-at-wake-island.aspx}}</ref>。估计威克岛一共因这场台风受到价值8800万美元（2006年美元）的破坏<ref>{{cite web|author=Advisory Council for Historic Preservation |year=2007 |title=Spring 2007 Case Digest — Protecting Historic Properties |accessdate=2016-03-18 |url=http://www.achp.gov/docs/case_spring_07small.pdf |format=PDF |page=17 |archivedate=2015-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715131945/http://achp.gov/docs/case_spring_07small.pdf |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 日本和阿拉斯加州 ===
[[File:Ioke_2006-09-07_1300Z.png|thumb]]上空]]
面对台风威胁，日本气象厅于9月1日下令[[南鸟岛|南鸟岛]]上的工作人员临时撤离<ref>{{cite web | author = Japan Meteorological Agency | year = 2006 | title = Evacuation of Minami Torishima during Typhoon Ioke | accessdate = 2016-03-18 | url = http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/press/0609/01a/marcus.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222919/http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/press/0609/01a/marcus.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。岛上设施受到破坏，但在风暴过去三周内就已修复并全面恢复正常运作<ref>{{cite web | author = Japan Meteorological Agency | year = 2006 | title = About Weather Observation Reopening of the South Torishima Meteorological Observing Station | accessdate = 2016-03-19 | url = http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/press/0609/29a/marcus.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110322200358/http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/press/0609/29a/marcus.html | archivedate = 2011-03-22 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

伊欧凯的温带残留在阿拉斯加州西南海岸沿线产生风暴潮和超过9.1米高的狂浪，再加上[[潮汐|天文高潮]]推波助澜，阿拉斯加州的[[布里斯托尔湾_(阿拉斯加)|布里斯托尔湾]]和[[育空-卡斯科奎姆河三角洲|育空-卡斯科奎姆河三角洲]]因此出现轻度洪灾<ref name="ncdc">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2006 | title = Event Report for Alaska | accessdate = 2009-07-28 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~604224 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090728173708/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~604224  | archivedate = 2009-07-28 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，[[乌纳拉斯卡_(阿拉斯加州)|乌纳拉斯卡]]的最强阵风时速达135公里<ref name="ncdc2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2006 | title = Event Report for Alaska (2) | accessdate = 2008-05-30 | archivedate = 2008-05-30 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~604225 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080530001922/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~604225}}</ref>。气旋令阿拉斯加州西部普降中到大雨，[[伯特利_(阿拉斯加州)|伯特利]]和[[科策布_(阿拉斯加州)|科策布]]的日降雨量分别有29和17毫米，均创下新纪录。该州东南部也出现降水，[[朱诺_(阿拉斯加州)|朱诺]]附近地区的降雨总量因此高于正常水平。<ref name="cattlenet">{{cite news | author = Cattle Network | year = 2006 | title = National Weather early for September 2006 | accessdate = 2009-07-27 | url = http://www.cattlenetwork.com/content.asp?contentid=67684 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090727143242/http://www.cattlenetwork.com/content.asp?contentid=67684 | archivedate = 2009-07-27 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>

== 所创纪录及善后 ==
[[File:Ioke-wake-damage003.jpg|thumb]]
飓风伊欧凯是有纪录以来中北太平洋形成的五场[[五级太平洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]之一，也是唯一一个在该海域成形的。估计风暴中心最低气压仅915毫巴（百帕，27.019[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），比有纪录以来中太平洋出现过的其它任何热带气旋都要低<ref name="tcr" />，打破[[1994年太平洋飓风季|1994年]][[飓风约翰_(1994年)|飓风约翰]]所创纪录<ref>{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | year = 2007 | title = Northeast Pacific Ocean Tropical Cyclone Best Track | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2016-03-19 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/NEpacifichurdat.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200223/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/NEpacifichurdat.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03}}</ref>。伊欧凯在四级或以上强度（持续风速每小时至少211公里）连续保持了198小时之久，比有纪录以来地球上其它任何热带气旋都要久<ref name="tcr" />。此外，气旋还在超级台风强度下连续保持174小时之久，创下又一项纪录<ref name="gp" />。由于风暴持续时间特别长，强度也特别高，其[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]高达82，再刷新一项纪录<ref>{{cite web|author1=Mark Saunders |author2=Adam Lea |year=2007 |title=Summary of 2006 NW Pacific Typhoon Season and Verification of Authors’ Seasonal Forecasts |publisher=Tropical Storm Risk |accessdate=2016-03-19 |url=http://tsr.mssl.ucl.ac.uk/docs/TSRNWP2006Verification.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210855/http://tsr.mssl.ucl.ac.uk/docs/TSRNWP2006Verification.pdf |format=PDF |archivedate=2016-03-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

台风过去3天后，[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]于9月2日从空中对威克岛所受破坏程度开展首轮评估。评估结果表明岛上总体破坏程度低于预期，没有出现石油或有害物质泄露。9月7日，海岸警卫队派出工作组乘船抵达威克岛，工作组在4天后完成评估报告，他们还修好一台发电机用于供电。<ref name="afd" />[[美国海军|美国海军]]圣何塞号（{{lang|en|San Jose}}）同[[美国空军|美国空军]]第36应急响应组的16名成员于9月8日抵达该岛，并在核心试验人员清理跑道允许通航后分析机场是否能稳定运作，同时协助清理工作<ref>{{cite web|author=Chris Johnson |year=2006 |title=In the Wake of Ioki |publisher=U.S. Military |archivedate=2016-03-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193806/http://www.msc.navy.mil/sealift/2006/November/ioki.htm |accessdate=2016-03-19 |url=http://www.msc.navy.mil/sealift/2006/November/ioki.htm }}</ref>。在多名工程师的共同努力下，岛上供电于9月13日恢复<ref>{{cite news | author = Chris Vadnais | date = 2006-09-20 | title = Power pros 'wire' Wake Island | publisher = Air Force Print News | accessdate = 2008-09-11 | url = http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123027497 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080911184809/http://www.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123027497 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2008-09-11}}</ref>。伊欧凯过去约两周后，多幢建筑都已恢复正常运作<ref name="afd2" />。

2007年4月，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]应中太平洋飓风中心的请求将风暴名称“伊欧凯”（{{lang|en|Ioke}}）除名，以“伊欧帕”（{{lang|en|Iopa}}）取代<ref>{{cite report|author=Advisory Council for Historic Preservation |date=2007-05-07 |title=Spring 2007 Case Digest — Protecting Historic Properties section 106 in action |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.achp.gov/docs/case_spring_07small.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2015-08-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715131945/http://achp.gov/docs/case_spring_07small.pdf |archivedate=2015-07-15 }}</ref>。

